msgstr "Vitaj vo WiVRn"

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:69
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This wizard will help you set up WiVRn on your headset and connect it to "
"your computer."
msgstr ""
"Tento sprievodca vám pomôže nastaviť WiVRn na vašom headsete a pripojiť ho k "
"počítaču."

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:83 dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:258
#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:418 dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:455
