#, kde-format
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Riešenie problémov"

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:358
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If the server is not visible or the connection fails, check that ports 5353 "
"(UDP) and 9757 (TCP and UDP) are open in your firewall."
msgstr ""
"Ak server nie je viditeľný alebo pripojenie zlyhá, skontrolujte, či máte vo fi"
"rewalle povolené porty 5353 (UDP) a 9757 (TCP aj UDP)."

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:371
#, kde-format
msgid "Skip"
msgstr "Preskočiť"

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:391
#, kde-format
msgid "Connection established"
msgstr "Pripojenie nadviazané"

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:396
#, kde-format
msgid "Your headset is now connected."
msgstr "Headset je teraz pripojený."

#: dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:401 dashboard/qml/WizardPage.qml:443
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To connect another headset, make sure pairing is enabled in the dashboard "
"before connecting."
msgstr ""
"Ak chcete pripojiť ďalší headset, uistite sa, že je v ovládacom paneli "
"povolené párovanie."

